SUBENT        F0914003   20251227   20260311   20260311       F107
BIB                  5         11
REACTION   (22-TI-48(A,INL)22-TI-48,,DE)
ANALYSIS   The data on the scattering cross sections for alpha-
           particles in gold were used to calibrate the relative
           measurements. For this goal alpha-particle scattering
           by an Au target over the angular range 20-60. degr.
           was measured.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) No information about source of uncertainty
STATUS     (CURVE,,A.E.Antropov+,J,BAS,46,(1),169,1982) Fig.1(b)
           (DEP,F0914002) The relative measurements of
           alpha-particle scattering by 48T1.
HISTORY    (20251227U) SD: BIB updated. MISC-ERR -> E-ERR-DIG.
